## 6. Conclusion

In this article, the reaction rate in chemical kinetics was analyzed by taking the form of uncertain differential equation, and the modeling process of uncertain chemical reaction equation was presented. Furthermore, the method of moments was used to estimate the parameters involved from the observations. The derived model, with the estimated parameters, performed well in fitting the observations. Half-life of reaction has been developed to discover how quickly the concentration of the reactant decreased. Finally, a paradox associated with stochastic chemical kinetics was introduced.

